a new classification of cachexia subtypes.

826
00:46:39.623 --> 00:46:42.924
So in preliminary baseline analysis of patient-reported outcomes,

827
00:46:43.424 --> 00:46:46.994
symptom clusters among those classically characterized as

828
00:46:47.044 --> 00:46:50.444
cachexia emerge, including a cluster of relatively

